title: Daily Wire Backstage: Live at the Ryman
description:
Join Daily Wire god-king Jeremy Boreing and hosts Ben Shapiro, Candace Owens, Michael Knowles, Matt Walsh, and Andrew Klavan LIVE at the Ryman as they tackle today’s big political and cultural issues, host musical guests — and unveil several surprise announcements you won’t want to miss! 
Daily Wire members were the first to get tickets to our Nashville event. Join Daily Wire for 25% off with code BACKSTAGE for exclusive offers! JOIN: https://utm.io/udQrK
